26#pragma once
27
28#include "CachedFont.h"
29#include "CachedFontClient.h"
30#include "CachedResourceHandle.h"
31#include "FontLoadRequest.h"
32#include "FontSelectionAlgorithm.h"
33
34namespace WebCore {
35
36class CachedFontLoadRequest final : public FontLoadRequest, public CachedFontClient {
37 WTF_MAKE_FAST_ALLOCATED;
38public:
39 CachedFontLoadRequest(CachedFont& font)
40 : m_font(&font)
41 {
42 }
43
44 ~CachedFontLoadRequest()
45 {
46 if (m_fontLoadRequestClient)
47 m_font->removeClient(*this);
48 }
49
50 CachedFont& cachedFont() const { return *m_font; }
51
52private:
53 const URL& url() const final { return m_font->url(); }
54 bool isPending() const final { return m_font->status() == CachedResource::Status::Pending; }
55 bool isLoading() const final { return m_font->isLoading(); }
56 bool errorOccurred() const final { return m_font->errorOccurred(); }
57
58 bool ensureCustomFontData(const AtomString& remoteURI) final { return m_font->ensureCustomFontData(remoteURI); }
59 RefPtr<Font> createFont(const FontDescription& description, const AtomString& remoteURI, bool syntheticBold, bool syntheticItalic, const FontFeatureSettings& settings, FontSelectionSpecifiedCapabilities capabilities) final
60 {
61 return m_font->createFont(description, remoteURI, syntheticBold, syntheticItalic, settings, capabilities);
62 }
63
64 void setClient(FontLoadRequestClient* client) final
65 {
66 auto* oldClient = m_fontLoadRequestClient;
67 m_fontLoadRequestClient = client;
68
69 if (!client && oldClient)
70 m_font->removeClient(*this);
71 else if (client && !oldClient)
72 m_font->addClient(*this);
73 }
74
75 bool isCachedFontLoadRequest() const final { return true; }
76
77 void fontLoaded(CachedFont& font) final
78 {
79 ASSERT_UNUSED(font, &font == m_font.get());
80 if (m_fontLoadRequestClient)
81 m_fontLoadRequestClient->fontLoaded(*this);
82 }
83
84 CachedResourceHandle<CachedFont> m_font;
85 FontLoadRequestClient* m_fontLoadRequestClient { nullptr };
86};
87
88} // namespace WebCore
89
90SPECIALIZE_TYPE_TRAITS_FONTLOADREQUEST(WebCore::CachedFontLoadRequest, isCachedFontLoadRequest())
